<ENAMEX TYPE="ORG">National Convenience Stores Inc.</ENAMEX> , trying to shake the doldrums in the convenience - store business , said it will rearrange the merchandise in all of its stores in <ENAMEX TYPE="DATE">the next 18 months</ENAMEX> to cater better to the neighborhoods around its stores .
