<ENAMEX TYPE="ORG">National Convenience 's</ENAMEX> move is likely to be echoed by other chains , though analysts note that <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG">Southland Corp.</ENAMEX> , owner of <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG">7 - Eleven</ENAMEX> stores , and <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG">Circle K Corp.</ENAMEX> are too debt - heavy to roll out such an extensive effort .
